          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">PCG</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:middle;">
          <para styleclass="Table Header"><text styleclass="Table Header" translate="true">Purpose</text></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The Preconditioned Conjugate-Gradient package is used to solve the finite difference equations in each step of a MODFLOW stress period.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
